Package com.stockticker.logic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AuthorizationService
    This is the interface defines the functionality for user authorization.
    StockHistoryService
    This is the interface that defines the methods provided to retrieve stock history.
    StockQuoteService
    This is the interface defines the functionality for stock quote services.
    StockTickerService
    This interface defines the functionality to get tracked stocks.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    BusinessLogicService
    This class provides the functionality to initialize and get the services for the Business Logic.
    StockTicker
    This class provides the basic functionality of getting stock quotes, tracking, and un-tracking stocks for users.
    UserAuthorization
    This class provides user authorization functionality.
    YahooStockHistoryService
    This class provides stock history service from Yahoo.
    YahooStockQuoteService
    This class gets Yahoo stock quotes from the web.
